OL,4,G1045FRip Off Britain
OL,5,     GThe team investigate the
OL,6,     Gmysterious transactions made via
OL,7,     Gmobile phone payments - even
OL,8,     Gafter the customer had cancelled
OL,9,     Gtheir bank card.
OL,10,G1115FHomes Under the Hammer
OL,11,     GWe head to the Kent coast to
OL,12,     Grevisit a renovation that's taken
OL,13,     Gsome time to finish. Jacqui
OL,14,     Gchecks out a large terrace as
OL,15,     Gwell as a tiny flat in a tale of
OL,16,     Gtwo contrasting projects.
OL,17,G1215FBargain Hunt
OL,18,     GAs the red and blue teams vie for
OL,19,     Gvictory, Eric Knowles remembers
OL,20,     Gthe day when Llanelli defeated
OL,21,     Gthe mighty All Blacks in one of
OL,22,     Grugby's famous upsets.
